These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Movie-Genre: animation, documentary, drama, time-travel
Sport: cycling, ice-hockey, soccer, weightlifting
1. Movie-Genre:animation is on the right of Sport:soccer##1
2. Sport:weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. Sport:soccer is between Sport:ice-hockey and Movie-Genre:documentary##2
4. Movie-Genre:time-travel is on the far left##1
5. Movie-Genre:drama is between Movie-Genre:documentary and Movie-Genre:animation##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel         | documentary   | drama | animation       |
| Sport      | weightlifting | cycling | soccer   | ice-hockey |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
City: boston, prague, london, paris
1. City:paris is between Hobby:reading and City:prague##2
2. Hobby:video-games is on the far right##1
3. City:london is on the right of City:boston##1
4. Hobby:gardening is on the left of City:boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| City   | prague    | paris   | boston | london       |

