2. Nationality:colombian is between Nationality:british and Transport:skateboard##2
3. Nationality:british is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:french is on the left of Transport:tram##1
5. Transport:skateboard == Nationality:french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Transport          | van    | airplane | skateboard   | tram  |
| Nationality   | british | colombian   | french | australian |

